Package org.openwms.core.search

Class Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openwms.core.search.Action
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class Action
extends Object
implements Serializable
    An Action represents a possible UI action an User can take. Each Action has a resulting URL to a webpage and a descriptive text that is displayed in the UI. Additionally a field weight is used to count how many times the User has chosen this Action.
    Since:
    0.2
    Version:

    Author:

    • Method Detail

      • rate

        public int rate​(String... words)
        Calculate and return a rating for a list of words. Every match between a word and one of the tags, increases the rating. In case none of the tags matches, 0 is returned.
        Parameters:
        words - The Array of words to calculate the rating
        Returns:
        0 when none of the words matches, or any other positive value in case of matches
